planning_data.dds_location_mapping_upload:
# dds_location_mapping_upload.cfg

# end point of the HAFAS HUB
DDS_CFG_URL=https://sncb-opendata.hafas.de/dds-rest

# API version used by the HAFAS HUB
DDS_CFG_API_VERSION=0.7

# IDs and names of the station list
DDS_CFG_MASTER_DATA_LIST_ID=46567684455
DDS_CFG_MASTER_DATA_LIST_NAME=stoppoints.csv

# List of all mapping tables used in the HAFAS HUB with IDs and names
# 
# Here sample values are used. IDs and names have to be determined as 
# described in section 2.2
#
# 
DDS_CFG_MAPPING_ID_LIST_1=46567684457:matching_table_platforms

# List of IDs of the corrsponding satellite systems <satelliteID> as 
# described in section 3.3:
#  
DDS_CFG_SATELLITE_SYSTEM_ID_LIST=46567684421
